{"tid":516081,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"藝人向佐元旦駕Benz跑失控 撼2車傷2女途人","createTime":"2018-01-01T04:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T05:05:34.000Z","uid":156068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"daaeb70df3482b2e940f7336f5f6c1b67d18e656","tid":516081,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:52:21.000Z","msg":"藝人向佐尖沙咀駕Benz跑發生意外，撞車撞傷途人。今晨4時許，向佐(33歲)駕駛一輛黑色Benz跑沿金巴利道駛至近天文臺道，突然失控撞向路邊一輛寶馬房車，並將其推前前撞向前面一輛四驅車尾部，釀成3車串燒。2名女途人剛巧在兩車之間橫過馬路，閃避不及，腳部同被夾傷，有途人目睹代為報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，向佐未有受傷，2名受傷女途人分別姓邱及姓陳，俱25歲，由救護車送院治理，警方事後聯絡被撞兩車車主助查。<br />\n<br />\n此外，肇事Benz跑於02年首次登記，車價逾130萬港元，由一間電影公司持有。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/01/125219_0645d235cd0d32db8da25d17c8b4af85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F01%2F125219_0645d235cd0d32db8da25d17c8b4af85.jpg&h=19ee2d14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2f93f7141534fe9b98a7db969601c269b8b649d","tid":516081,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:57:11.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"e54ff54f72674ab13f2c7d5c1fd19d568d5fae08","tid":516081,"uid":136430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:58:09.000Z","msg":"我睇咗Benz雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0837383d152ffca6cb4537e94301fd954035b66","tid":516081,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:59:42.000Z","msg":"我渣gtr我洗炒？"},{"pid":"0bb3e05bb6cacfb6d20be6b4151901f02125da90","tid":516081,"uid":29011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T05:02:19.000Z","msg":"响我暴龍哥個朵"},{"pid":"b776659b861b51850ae69b1a580d106903b21417","tid":516081,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"邊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p